nvidia-graphics-drivers (384.00-0ubuntu1) trusty; urgency=medium

  * Correct EGL libraries and glvnd loader script.
    - libEGL.so.XXX.YY is the old EGL interface. If it's present, libEGL.so
      and libEGL.so.1 should both link to libEGL.so.XXX.YY.
    - libEGL.so.1 is the new EGL interface, and only requires libEGL.so to
      link to it.
    - This commit removes libEGL.so.XXX.YY from the package. It also correctly
      includes 10_nvidia.json at /usr/share/glvnd/egl_vendor.d so that the EGL
      loader is aware of the NV-provided EGL vendor library.

 -- Andy Dick <adick@nvidia.com>  Fri, 21 Oct 2016 15:53:26 -0700

